With this blockbox from Mickey Mouse and his friends, your little one can recognize shapes and fine motor skills are stimulated. The blocks can be stacked on top of each other.

Color: multicolor
Material: wood
Dimensions: 12 x 12 x 46 cm (L x W x H)

5 Sticking out moulds
